The Princess Royal is very resourceful.

13
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:32,039
She'll likely hear

14
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:33,880
about Princess Fuqing
regaining her sight soon.

15
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:37,039
How will you explain yourself by then?

16
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,560
Saintess, don't worry.

17
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,080
I know how to deal with it.

18
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,520
Let me ask you something.

19
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,360
My mother,

20
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,320
the Countess,

21
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:49,920
Su Ke,

22
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,440
were you the one who killed her?

23
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,920
It was the Princess Royal.

24
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,280
She died due to Nanwu's Eternal Slumber.

25
00:02:08,210 --> 00:02:12,210
[Eternal Joy and Serenity]

26
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,440
Your Highness, you mustn't.

27
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,800
You just regained your sight
not long ago.

28
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,160
You mustn't be exposed to strong light.

29
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,800
You should remove it in a few more days.

30
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,079
Nanny Hua.

31
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,200
I wish to be alone for a while.

32
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:26,800
Yes, Your Highness.

33
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,040
What about Princess Fuqing?

34
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,720
She was just a young girl back then.

35
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,680
Why did you do that to her?

36
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,800
It's because she found out

37
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,560
about Princess Royal's darkest secrets.

38
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:16,380
[Eternal Joy and Serenity]

39
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,880
Your Highness, let's rest inside.

40
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,400
You've just regained your vision.

41
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:21,960
You have plenty of time.

42
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,320
You can take your time to view the sun.

43
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,840
I'm worried
that if I don't enjoy it now,

44
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,760
I won't be able to...

45
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,480
That won't happen.

46
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:29,920
You don't need to fear.

47
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,720
However, Your Highness,

48
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,960
I can only cure your eyes.

49
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,800
Other people cannot help you

50
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,600
conquer the fear in your heart.

51
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:44,160
In order to get rid of the nightmares,

52
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,840
we have to face the truth bravely.

53
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:52,010
[Princess Royal's Mansion]

54
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,880
Did you even do your job?

55
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,960
Why is Jiang Si still alive?

56
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,440
I failed in my duty.

57
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,520
I was just about to succeed.

58
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,880
But coincidentally,

59
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,440
His Majesty and Prince Yan

60
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,640
arrived at Changning Palace
at the same time.

61
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,080
If I acted back then,

62
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,520
I would've given myself away.

63
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,600
I've kept you by my side all these years

64
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:11,720
because

65
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,400
you did things neatly and swiftly.

66
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,079
This time, not only have you failed,

67
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:19,720
but Jiang Si also found out
about the Blind Bug,

68
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,040
curing Fuqing's eyes in the process.

69
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,760
What exactly is going on?

70
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,640
Your Highness, you don't need to worry.

71
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,720
I think Prince Yan
picked up some tricks from Nanwu

72
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,480
when he was stationed there.

73
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,760
That's why he cured the princess' eyes.

74
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,760
They told His Majesty
that they merely found

75
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,800
a folk prescription.

76
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,080
They didn't mention anything
related to Nanwu.

77
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,640
If so,

78
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,400
does that mean they didn't suspect you?

79
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:42,440
Yes.

80
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,760
Mother, Si is right.

81
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,000
If I keep hiding the secrets,

82
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,840
even if I can see,

83
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,600
I cannot dispel

84
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,800
the fear in my heart.

85
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,159
Mother.

86
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,480
Someone

87
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,800
made me blind on purpose.

88
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,240
Really?

89
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:03,880
What exactly happened?

90
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,840
It's because I saw something

91
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,480
I wasn't supposed to.

92
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,000
[The 13th year of the Jingming era]
That day,

93
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,720
I was playing hide-and-seek
with my friends.

94
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,280
They locked me in the cabinet.

95
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,880
Empress Qingrong

96
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,200
opposes me at every turn.

97
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,360
She was arrogant as well.

98
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:23,080
She told me to be sensible
and move out of Ling'an.

99
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,480
If not, I won't be able to leave

100
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,440
once the Crown Prince
ascends the throne.

101
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,240
Since that's the case,

102
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,720
I'll make sure she dies

103
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,400
before the ascension ceremony.

104
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:40,880
I'll make sure she cannot enter
the imperial mausoleum after death.

105
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,880
The poison you mentioned before,

106
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,840
can it really make it

107
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,040
as if the victim died with symptoms
resembling leprosy?

108
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,520
Yes.

109
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:49,640
Excellent.

110
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,640
Tonight's the Double Ninth Festival.
Everyone is climbing to higher ground.

111
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,480
Poison her.

112
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:24,760
Fuqing.

113
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,400
What have you seen just now?

114
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:29,000
What have you heard?

115
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,640
I... I was asleep.

116
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,600
I didn't hear or see anything.

117
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,240
What a good girl.

118
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:39,680
You're so obedient.

119
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,440
If only Mingyue

120
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,120
was as obedient as you.

121
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,240
Tonight,

122
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,600
your father is releasing sky lanterns
at Zhengyang Tower.

123
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,880
Come on. I'll take you there.

124
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,200
I'm not going!

125
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,760
I want to find Mother!

126
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,880
She's already on her way here.

127
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,560
You'll be able to see her later.

128
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,240
I wish to give a good girl like you

129
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,160
a reward.

130
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,520
Why don't I make your mother

131
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,240
the new Empress?

132
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,440
Fuqing, come here.

133
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,920
May Zhou be blessed

134
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:28,160
with peace and prosperity.

135
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:30,120
- May Zhou be blessed
- May Zhou be blessed

136
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:33,360
- with peace and prosperity.
- with peace and prosperity.

137
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:36,040
So, that's how

138
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,320
I became the Empress.

139
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:44,920
I thought it was
because His Majesty favored me

140
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,960
and took pity on you
because you lost your sight.

141
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,240
The throne of the Empress,

142
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,880
the head of the six palaces,

143
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,080
I want none of that.

144
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,680
I only want my daughter

145
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,400
to be safe

146
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,920
and healthy.

147
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,280
Mother,
you don't need to blame yourself.

148
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:02,720
The one who started it all

149
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,040
was Princess Royal Rong Yang.

150
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,920
But you're her niece.

151
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,800
How could she do that?

152
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,000
Your Majesty.

153
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:11,760
She's not as benevolent or compassionate

154
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,560
as you.

155
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,280
Fuqing isn't the only victim.

156
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,040
I was a victim too.

157
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,640
To absolve Cui Xu of guilt,

158
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,560
she prevented my mother
from being promoted.

159
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,840
She even instructed
the Directorate of Astronomy

160
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,360
to fabricate a tale
of me being a bringer of misfortune.

161
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,840
Right after I was born,

162
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,480
I was sent to the Southern Frontier.

163
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,360
What?

164
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,560
She even dared to target the prince?

165
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:32,520
She has no regard for the law at all!

166
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:35,200
It's my fault for heeding your advice

167
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,679
and going easy on her.

168
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,559
I didn't get rid of that lass.

169
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,320
I only made her blind.

170
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:45,680
I even went out of my way

171
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:47,080
to grant her and her mother
overwhelming power

172
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,760
to compensate them.

173
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,160
I never expected

174
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,480
to bring ruin

175
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,280
upon myself.

176
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:57,560
If she tells people

177
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,760
about what I've done...

178
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,000
Your Highness,

179
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,560
the late Empress
has been dead for many years.

180
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,200
Besides,

181
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,520
who would believe

182
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,120
the words of a blind girl?

183
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,160
Wasn't that

184
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,960
why we made Princess Fuqing blind
in the first place?

185
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,080
I served Empress Di for many years.

186
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,160
I know her personality well.

187
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,920
Even if she knew about
the truth back then,

188
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,720
she would make her daughter

189
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,560
keep the secret.

190
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:25,280
Between a pair of eyes and her life,

191
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,320
I'm sure she knows
which is the better option.

192
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,920
Times have changed.

193
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:34,080
No matter how timid or inept she is,

194
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,600
she's been the Empress for many years.

195
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,920
Power

196
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,880
is what blinds people the most.

197
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,760
It makes them forget who they are.

198
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,200
What if we compare her

199
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,240
to the late Empress
who was at the height

200
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,040
of her power?

201
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,200
Who's better?

202
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,200
You're right.

203
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,920
I lost my composure just now.

204
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,520
I need to let them know

205
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:04,560
who my brother cares about

206
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:08,240
and believes the most.

207
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:11,080
The Empress and Yu Jin,

208
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:14,240
who do they think they are?

209
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,400
We can't afford to let Princess Royal

210
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,960
harm the Imperial Palace

211
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:18,920
and the innocent again.

212
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,120
If we report her

213
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,240
to His Majesty together

214
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,040
and reopen the case
of the late Empress' death,

215
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,160
the Crown Prince

216
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,320
will stop supporting her.

217
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,120
Only by bringing her to justice

218
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,200
can Princess Fuqing

219
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,720
truly be at peace

220
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,320
and be rid of the nightmares
that haunt her.

221
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,040
This won't do.

222
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,080
Mother?

223
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,520
Fuqing has lost her sight for ten years.

224
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,920
Do you intend
to let her off just like that?

225
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,440
I can endure everything

226
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:46,160
as long as Fuqing is safe.

227
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:50,120
Before this, the late Empress
pitted herself against her.

228
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,360
She even had the Crown Prince's backing.

229
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,920
But what happened to her in the end?

230
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,520
She didn't do anything wrong,

231
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,560
yet she suffered a terrible death.

232
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,800
I've lived in this palace

233
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,120
for many years.

234
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,360
Although I'm not capable,

235
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,880
there's one thing

236
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:10,560
I understand clearly.

237
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:13,600
To His Majesty, the Princess Royal

238
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,280
is different from everyone else.

239
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:19,440
Although she's not
his biological sister,

240
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,560
they grew up

241
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,720
and went through
thick and thin together.

242
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,480
She even protected him

243
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:26,600
during Prince Xiang's rebellion.

244
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,080
She risked her own life

245
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,560
to rescue His Majesty.

246
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,080
Forget about Fuqing.

247
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:35,000
Even the Crown Prince and Prince Qi

248
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,200
cannot compare to her weight

249
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,280
in His Majesty's heart.

250
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,040
If it doesn't concern one's life,

251
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,720
you should tolerate it.

252
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,960
Once you get married,

253
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,520
you can form your family

254
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,720
and lead your own life.

255
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:49,960
Do not pit yourself against her.

256
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:50,960
But Your Majesty...

257
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,080
Your Majesty, we understand

258
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:53,440
your intentions.

259
00:11:58,800 --> 00:11:59,440
Mother.

260
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,000
Mother, have you heard?

261
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,880
Jiang Si actually found
a folk prescription

262
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,760
that cured Princess Fuqing's eyes.

263
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:08,960
She was blind for many years.

264
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,720
Now, Uncle

265
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,800
will only favor her even more.

266
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:13,400
Do you still have a way

267
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:15,000
to make Uncle change his mind?

268
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:16,320
Am I no longer able

269
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,240
to be married to Yu Jin?

270
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,160
If that's the case,

271
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,600
I don't want to live anymore!

272
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:24,880
You only talk about Yu Jin.

273
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:27,160
Do you even remember

274
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:28,200
that my birth date is nearing?

275
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:36,680
I...

276
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:40,760
Uncle

277
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:41,760
celebrates your birthday

278
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:42,840
with us every year.

279
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:46,440
I've never begged anyone in my life,

280
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,480
including my brother.

281
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,520
This time, I'm doing it for you.

