00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:54,320
Thank you, Mother.

283
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:00,720
To uproot a corrupted pillar

284
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,640
like the Princess Royal

285
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,400
isn't as simple as I think.

286
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:05,360
If I hadn't

287
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,360
revealed my identity
in front of Nanny Duo,

288
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,280
I wouldn't have to be

289
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,320
so cautious now.

290
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,240
You've already done a great job.

291
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:13,560
Don't blame yourself.

292
00:13:14,880 --> 00:13:16,360
Judging from Her Majesty's attitude,

293
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:17,520
even if

294
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:19,000
we present Nanny Duo

295
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,200
to her,

296
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:21,040
she won't

297
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,280
pit herself against the Princess Royal.

298
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,400
But someone needs
to take the first step somehow.

299
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:28,960
There are certain things
that have to be done.

300
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,960
I thought Her Majesty

301
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:34,000
made a good point just now.

302
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:35,400
What point?

303
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:37,640
We have to lead our own lives.

304
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,240
We can't just focus on

305
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,280
our fight against the Princess Royal

306
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,160
until we forget about our wedding.

307
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,160
The Office of Ceremonies

308
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,400
will handle the wedding.

309
00:13:45,880 --> 00:13:47,320
They're well-versed and experienced.

310
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,640
Don't tell me

311
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,720
we need to take it to hand.

312
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,200
Have you learned palace etiquette?

313
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,720
It's just a ruse.

314
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:53,920
Besides,

315
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,000
if I do take it seriously,

316
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,440
I'm sure I can master it quickly.

317
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:57,520
Have you tried the wedding gown?

318
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,280
No.

319
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:01,960
What about the furniture
and decoration of my mansion?

320
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,360
You're the future female head there.

321
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:07,200
Do I need to pick them personally?

322
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,480
But the current furniture
and decoration there

323
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,600
look pretty good to me.

324
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,480
Is that so, huh?

325
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,760
You're just afraid of trouble.

326
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:16,040
This is our wedding.

327
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,360
It's the most important event

328
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:19,120
of our lives.

329
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,480
Of course I hope

330
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,880
that you're happy with the mansion,

331
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:24,160
the banquet,

332
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:26,200
and the wedding gown you wear.

333
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,240
Most importantly,

334
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:31,120
I'm happy with my groom.

335
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:38,200
[Crown Prince's Mansion]

336
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,040
Your Highness.

337
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:40,680
I've fasted for three days

338
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:41,960
and copied this Diamond Sutra

339
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:42,840
myself.

340
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:46,040
For birthday gifts,
it's the thought that counts.

341
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:47,800
[Diamond Sutra]
A sutra?

342
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,400
Aunt never liked

343
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,280
chanting sutras or praying to Buddha.

344
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:51,200
I'm afraid

345
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:53,400
she won't like something like this.

346
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,080
Your Highness, what about this?

347
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,560
This is the Tree of Prosperity.

348
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:58,290
It's a gift
from the Commander of Xiling.

349
00:14:58,290 --> 00:14:59,760
[Crown Princess]
It's a gift
from the Commander of Xiling.

350
00:14:59,760 --> 00:14:59,930
[Crown Princess]

351
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:02,320
It implies prosperity and fortune.

352
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:03,480
My dear, I'm afraid you forgot

353
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:05,120
that we gave her the same gift

354
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,320
three years ago.

355
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,520
This isn't sincere enough.

356
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:14,320
All of these won't do.

357
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,120
All of you, leave.

358
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:20,440
Your Highness,

359
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,600
it's just a birthday gift.

360
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:24,320
If you don't like them,

361
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:25,840
I can prepare something else.

362
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,440
You don't need to be this nervous.

363
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:28,680
How could I not?

364
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,000
After Mother's passing,

365
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,560
Imperial Concubine Xian
tried multiple times

366
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:32,520
to do me in

367
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:33,720
so that Zhang could

368
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,160
take my place.

369
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:36,400
Did you forget about that?

370
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:38,240
I dare not.

371
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,960
You couldn't take walnuts.

372
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:42,080
But she mixed

373
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:44,080
crushed walnuts

374
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:45,120
into your snacks.

375
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:46,960
You almost died because of it.

376
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,880
The Princess Royal rescued you

377
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,280
and reported it to His Majesty.

378
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:51,560
Only then
was Imperial Concubine Xian punished.

379
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:52,920
That's precisely it.

380
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:54,640
I'm only able

381
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:55,720
to retain my position

382
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:58,000
all because Aunt let go
of the grudge she had against Mother.

383
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,640
Zhang has been competing

384
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,440
with me all these years,

385
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:03,160
but he never got the upper hand.

386
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:03,840
Why?

387
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:06,080
It's because Aunt

388
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,760
was supporting me.

389
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,640
Your Highness, you're right.

390
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:15,200
I'll remember it.

391
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,240
Greetings, Your Highness.

392
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:19,200
The Princess Royal's servants
notified us

393
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,280
that she wouldn't be holding

394
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:20,840
a birthday celebration this year.

395
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:22,360
She's not having one?

396
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,880
But she holds it every year.

397
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,360
I'm sure Mingyue has annoyed her so much

398
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:29,720
that she's in no mood to hold it.

399
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,080
It's all Jin's fault.

400
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,240
Since that's the case,

401
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:34,160
Your Highness,

402
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:36,520
there's no need
to prepare any birthday gifts.

403
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,600
If she's not holding a celebration,

404
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:41,600
the gifts have to be extra special.

405
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:43,640
Forget it.

406
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:44,600
I'll prepare it myself.

407
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:49,080
You only remember your aunt's birthday.

408
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,600
But you've already forgotten about

409
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,080
your mother's death anniversary.

410
00:16:56,190 --> 00:16:59,890
[Princess Royal's Mansion]

411
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,640
Why is there no one here?

412
00:17:22,319 --> 00:17:23,480
Today's her birthday.

413
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:25,240
Look at how desolate the place is.

414
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,160
Perhaps Her Highness
is at the pavilion...

415
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:34,560
Rong Yang.

416
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:37,480
Brother.

417
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:39,800
Today's your birthday.

418
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:41,280
Why are you

419
00:17:41,280 --> 00:17:42,800
drinking at the pavilion alone?

420
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:44,400
Brother,

421
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,920
you're the only person

422
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:47,640
who remembers my birthday now.

423
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,080
Nonsense.

424
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,400
What about your husband,

425
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:52,400
your daughter,

426
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,920
and your servants?

427
00:17:58,520 --> 00:18:00,360
I have nothing left.

428
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:01,880
Cui Xu has left me.

429
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:04,520
I raised Mingyue in vain.

430
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,680
She argued with me

431
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,920
because of a man.

432
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:12,440
People see the Princess Royal's Mansion
as a fancy place,

433
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:15,760
yet no one knows how tragic I am.

434
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:17,920
Here.

435
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:19,600
Brother.

436
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,400
Let's have a toast.

437
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,760
Do you still remember
this outfit of mine?

438
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:42,080
Of course.

439
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:44,760
You wore this

440
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:47,160
to lure Prince Xiang's rebel army away

441
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:47,920
back then.

442
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,680
I was only able

443
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:51,560
to assume my throne

444
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:52,440
all because you risked your life.

445
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,320
Without you,

446
00:18:55,600 --> 00:18:56,400
I'm afraid

447
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,520
Prince Xiang would've been

448
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:00,000
in my place.

449
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:02,160
I never regretted it,

450
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,160
even when

451
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,520
Prince Xiang

452
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:07,640
hung me on the city wall

453
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:09,440
for three days and nights.

454
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,720
It's not because of Zhou

455
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,720
or the throne.

456
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:15,200
It's because you're my only brother.

457
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:18,280
You're the dearest kin I have.

458
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:22,840
Rong Yang.

459
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:26,120
In this world,

460
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,880
only you are truly sincere to me.

461
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:33,360
You're my dearest kin.

462
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,680
I have no regrets

463
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:47,640
even if I have to die for your sake.

464
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,080
Stop right there!

465
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,080
Who's inside?

466
00:19:53,140 --> 00:19:53,780
[Changning Palace]

467
00:19:53,780 --> 00:19:54,840
We're heading out
to tend to some affairs

468
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,720
under Her Majesty's order.

469
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:56,960
Do not ask questions.

470
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:03,040
Your Highness, we're leaving the palace.

471
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:04,480
Please sit tight.

472
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:06,040
Her Majesty permitted you
to talk a walk outside

473
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:07,160
without His Majesty's knowledge.

474
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,680
She instructed me

475
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,720
to keep a low profile
and ensure your safety.

476
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:11,920
All right.

477
00:20:12,680 --> 00:20:14,400
Youtiao for sale!

478
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:15,920
Come on, miss.

479
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:17,520
Watch out for the cart.

480
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:19,680
Nanny Duo, look!

481
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,240
Excellent!

482
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:25,920
Bravo!

483
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:26,480
Be careful.

484
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:29,520
Handmade products.

485
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:31,040
Take a look.

486
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:31,720
Don't.

487
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:33,200
It might prick your hand.

488
00:20:33,840 --> 00:20:35,520
Ward off evil, pray for blessings,
romance, you name it.

489
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:37,600
Miss, which color do you like?

490
00:20:39,560 --> 00:20:40,000
Let me...

491
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:40,720
No.

492
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:44,280
They're nothing rare.

493
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,680
They're not worthy for you.

494
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:47,120
Let's go.

495
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,680
Fresh Bingyuanzi for sale!

496
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:52,440
Take a look!

497
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:53,800
[Bingyuanzi Drink]
Bingyuanzi!

498
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:56,560
I want the snow milk drink,

499
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,520
iced Bingyuanzi,

500
00:20:58,720 --> 00:20:59,040
and...

501
00:20:59,040 --> 00:20:59,520
No.

502
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:03,440
Street food is unhygienic.

503
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:05,000
You might get

504
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,120
a stomach ache.

505
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,920
But it's been a while.

506
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,280
It's time for us to eat.

507
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,840
Your Highness, please make do with this.

508
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:13,440
We shall have a proper meal
back in the palace.

509
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,760
I'll get you some warm water.

510
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:32,920
Wait for me here.

511
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:01,400
Is this his first time
submitting a report?

512
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,120
No.

513
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:03,960
Where is he?

514
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:05,920
Mr. Zhen, he's here.

515
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:09,000
I, Zhen Heng.

516
00:22:09,320 --> 00:22:10,000
I know of a kind of kite

517
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,040
that can speak.

518
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:12,400
Even if you can't see it,

519
00:22:12,520 --> 00:22:14,080
you can still hear where it flies.

520
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:20,400
Mr. Zhen!

521
00:22:25,760 --> 00:22:26,560
What are you doing here?

522
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:43,080
Well...

523
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,280
Can you see now?

524
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,920
How did you

525
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:49,960
regain your sight?

526
00:22:51,120 --> 00:22:52,800
Jiang Si cured it for me.

527
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:57,440
Did you leave the palace alone?

528
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:58,160
No.

529
00:22:58,480 --> 00:22:59,960
I left the palace with Nanny.

530
00:23:00,320 --> 00:23:02,400
She said she went
to get some warm water.

531
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:04,000
She'll be back after a while.

532
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:05,880
Warm water?

533
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:07,840
She must've gone to one of the shops

534
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:09,040
along the street.

535
00:23:10,280 --> 00:23:10,680
Someone.

536
00:23:11,800 --> 00:23:13,240
Find Nanny Hua for the Princess.

537
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:14,160
Yes, Mr. Zhen.

538
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:19,320
You're alone outside.

539
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,680
Your mother will be worried.

540
00:23:21,360 --> 00:23:21,960
Why don't I

541
00:23:22,840 --> 00:23:23,920
send you back first?

542
00:23:28,520 --> 00:23:30,360
Can I not return now?

543
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:32,320
Mother finally permitted me

544
00:23:32,320 --> 00:23:33,440
to leave the palace.

545
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:36,160
I wish to spend more time

546
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,120
outside.

547
00:23:38,040 --> 00:23:40,000
This way, I'll have pleasant memories

548
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:43,680
to hold on to
when I return to the palace.

549
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:50,120
Moreover, I'm not alone.

550
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:51,560
You're here with me.

551
00:23:56,800 --> 00:23:57,120
All right.

552
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,120
Let me take you somewhere.

553
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:00,800
Thank you, Master.

554
00:24:04,120 --> 00:24:05,200
Where are we?

555
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:07,000
Look at all the fish!

556
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:11,440
Your Highness, be careful.

557
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,320
This is

558
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:18,400
considered

559
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,200
one of my retreats.

560
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:21,320
Whenever I'm exhausted,

561
00:24:21,320 --> 00:24:22,160
I'll come here

562
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:24,080
alone.

563
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:27,120
I'll take half a day to unwind

564
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,360
and reorganize my thoughts.

565
00:24:30,760 --> 00:24:31,800
I'll resume
my investigations after that.

566
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,640
To me,

567
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,080
you're capable of anything.

568
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:36,440
It turns out

569
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:37,880
that you feel down sometimes.

570
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:41,440
Of course.

571
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:46,560
There are two sides

572
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,320
to every person

573
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,040
and every affair.

574
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,280
If there's a bright side,

575
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:54,880
naturally, there's a dark side.

576
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:00,440
Your Highness, you're allowed
to leave the palace now.

577
00:25:01,040 --> 00:25:01,920
You've regained your sight too.

578
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:04,560
Naturally, you can witness

579
00:25:04,880 --> 00:25:05,800
the beauty of the world.

580
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,360
But at the same time,

581
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:10,720
you'll witness
the unpleasant side of the world.

582
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:14,080
Your Highness,

583
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:16,400
if you do encounter that moment,

584
00:25:17,080 --> 00:25:17,880
please do not be afraid.

585
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:20,440
In my opinion,

586
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,360
any issues

587
00:25:23,120 --> 00:25:24,640
can be resolved

588
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:25,880
as long as you seek the truth.

589
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:28,520
What do you think?

590
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:33,200
Mr. Zhen, everyone said

591
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:35,520
that you were stubborn and inflexible.

592
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:37,240
But today,

593
00:25:37,280 --> 00:25:38,480
I've understood you a little better.

594
00:25:39,560 --> 00:25:40,880
You're trying

595
00:25:41,040 --> 00:25:42,600
to change
the unpleasant side of the world

596
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:43,520
so that everyone

597
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:45,200
can live happily under the sun.

598
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:48,400
That's why you have
to be determined and resolute

599
00:25:48,720 --> 00:25:50,400
for you to ward off the shadows.

600
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:53,560
To me,

601
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:56,680
the law is the light.

602
00:25:57,840 --> 00:26:00,640
It punishes evil and upholds goodness,
dispelling the shadows in the process.

603
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:13,280
What is this?

604
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,160
It's actually blinking.

605
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:16,440
These are fireflies.

606
00:26:17,600 --> 00:26:19,120
I heard that they guide people

607
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:21,600
during dark nights.

608
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,520
They light themselves up

609
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:26,760
in order to shine for others.

610
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:44,520
It can rest on your hand?

611
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:45,920
You see,

612
00:26:47,520 --> 00:26:50,280
what the heart longs for
will always echo back.

613
00:26:58,280 --> 00:26:58,720
Here.

614
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,080
Give it a try.

615
00:27:23,840 --> 00:27:24,560
Where did Mr. Zhen

616
00:27:24,560 --> 00:27:25,920
take Her Highness?

617
00:27:26,120 --> 00:27:27,200
The palace gate is closing soon.

618
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:28,440
Why isn't she back yet?

619
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:29,480
Nanny!

620
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:31,600
Your Highness!

621
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:34,440
You're finally back.

622
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:36,640
Mr. Zhen, it was fun today.

623
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,080
Thank you, Mr. Zhen.

624
00:27:38,520 --> 00:27:39,360
The palace gate will be closed soon.

625
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:40,840
I shall take Her Highness back.

626
00:27:41,080 --> 00:27:41,400
All right.

627
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:43,560
Nanny, I'll leave her to you.

628
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,000
Farewell, Princess Fuqing.

629
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:54,800
Nanny.

630
00:27:55,120 --> 00:27:56,120
What took you so long

631
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:57,360
this afternoon?

632
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,720
I waited for you for so long.

633
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:01,280
I broke a porcelain vase.

634
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:03,120
The shopkeeper wanted
to extort money from me.

635
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:04,720
He wasn't willing to let me leave.

636
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:06,480
Close the gates!

637
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:27,360
[Prince Yan's Mansion]

638
00:28:35,120 --> 00:28:36,320
Prince Yan, you're the only one

639
00:28:36,560 --> 00:28:37,480
who can come up

640
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:39,600
with something like a trial wedding.

641
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:44,320
The bride and groom,
proceed with the bowing ceremony.

642
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:45,310
First bow.

643
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:48,510
♪Through endless twists
in the mundane world♪

644
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:49,400
Bow again.

645
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:53,720
Bow to each other.

646
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:56,780
♪The heart grows tender and bitter♪

647
00:28:56,800 --> 00:28:57,560
Rise.

648
00:28:59,510 --> 00:29:01,040
♪I ask the Sun♪

649
00:29:01,710 --> 00:29:05,040
♪If the light has taken root♪

650
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:08,110
♪As it prospers,
our love story writes itself♪

651
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:11,200
Wash your hands and present the towels.

652
00:29:15,410 --> 00:29:18,980
♪We lock eyes
and promise to stay together forever♪

653
00:29:19,040 --> 00:29:22,120
Take your position
and perform the Tonglao ceremony.

654
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:29,240
♪Our inseparable souls
can weather all storms♪

655
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:34,280
Share the meal,
and be of one heart and mind.

656
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:36,380
♪The tapestry of destiny
is filled with our youth♪

657
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:39,210
♪Our blissful time together♪

658
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:41,210
♪Will lead us to the sea of stars♪

659
00:29:44,480 --> 00:29:46,440
The imperial decree has arrived!

660
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:52,120
Prince Yan, Yu Jin, accept the decree!

661
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:56,480
Prince Yan, Yu Jin,

662
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:59,200
has virtue and talent,
is diligent and steadfast,

663
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:02,040
has led the Red Plume Cavalry
to many victories,

664
00:30:02,280 --> 00:30:04,840
and solved numerous cases
in the Capital Administration Office.

665
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,960
He is filial to his parents,

666
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:09,080
and treats his siblings well.

667
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:10,880
He left the palace at a young age,

668
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:12,520
never having the chance
to fulfill his filial duties.

669
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:14,360
I feel guilty towards him.

670
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:17,560
Although I've granted Jiang Si,
the daughter of Count of Dongping,

671
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,400
to him as his principal consort,

672
00:30:20,120 --> 00:30:22,080
the Jiang family's status
is not prominent enough.

673
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:23,720
Therefore, I've selected

674
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:25,640
Princess Mingyue, the daughter

675
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,000
of Princess Royal,

676
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,240
to be your next consort.

677
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:31,520
The two consorts shall embrace
equal status.

678
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:33,560
The order shall be executed.

679
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,640
Your Highness, please accept the decree.

680
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,200
Long Dan! Prepare my horse!

681
00:30:44,320 --> 00:30:44,800
Yes, Chief!

682
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:46,920
Don't worry.

683
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:50,760
You're the only one I'll marry.

684
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:53,240
Wait for my return.

685
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,800
This is bad!
Someone has breached the palace gates!

686
00:31:02,840 --> 00:31:04,600
Sound the drums! Be on high alert!

687
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:12,640
Stop! That's the Seventh Prince.

688
00:31:15,120 --> 00:31:15,520
Your Majesty,

689
00:31:15,760 --> 00:31:17,280
the Seventh Prince has breached
five palace gates in a row

690
00:31:17,560 --> 00:31:18,640
[Tiande Hall]
and is rushing toward Tiande Hall!

691
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,780
[Zhengyang Gate]

692
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:35,000
Your Highness, His Majesty is busy.

693
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,760
Father, please rescind your decree!

694
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:37,240
Your Highness!

695
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:38,680
The imperial decree
is the mandate of heaven!

696
00:31:38,840 --> 00:31:40,400
How could you expect him to rescind it?

697
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:42,840
Father, please rescind your decree!

698
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:44,760
Your Highness,
you should be lucky that His Majesty

699
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:46,840
is granting you two consorts at once!

700
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:49,080
Father, please rescind your decree!

701
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:52,240
I beg you, Father,
reconsider your decree!

702
00:31:52,240 --> 00:31:53,040
Your Highness, you...

703
00:31:53,320 --> 00:31:55,040
Who summoned you here?

704
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:01,880
Father, please rescind your decree.

705
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:04,040
You breached five palace gates in a row.

706
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:05,640
What are you up to?

707
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:07,440
Such an event has never occurred

708
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:08,840
since the founding of Zhou.

709
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,600
This is the palace gate,
not your mansion's gate.

710
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:11,960
You don't get to come and go at will!

711
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:13,240
I...

712
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:15,320
I panicked.

713
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:17,760
That's why I forgot about the rules.

714
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:19,800
More like you forgot about

715
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:20,880
your own identity.

716
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:22,360
Do you still think

717
00:32:22,360 --> 00:32:23,800
that you're Yu Qi
from the Southern Frontier?

718
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:24,640
That's not the case!

719
00:32:24,800 --> 00:32:26,520
You are a prince, a royal member!

720
00:32:26,760 --> 00:32:27,600
Every official

721
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:29,320
has their eyes on you.

722
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:30,640
If news of this gets out,

723
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:31,880
how will they think of me?

724
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,080
If I can't even keep my son

725
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:33,680
in check,

726
00:32:33,840 --> 00:32:34,840
how can I rule the realm?

727
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:42,520
Look at yourself.

728
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:43,920
You actually breached

729
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:44,880
five palace gates in a row

730
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,640
because of your marriage.

731
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:47,480
Those who don't know any better

732
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:49,560
might think it was a rebellion.

733
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:50,680
I dare not.

734
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:51,160
Baoping!

735
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:53,360
What's the crime
of trespassing into the palace gates?

736
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:57,000
Tell us.

737
00:32:58,600 --> 00:32:59,160
Speak!

738
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:01,760
Your Majesty,

739
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:03,960
trespassing into the palace gates
is a capital offense.

740
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:05,320
And it implicates the family clan!

741
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:06,640
Is that so?

742
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,840
Yu Jin, you're something else.

743
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:09,680
Are you trying to kill me here?

744
00:33:09,720 --> 00:33:10,640
That was never my intention!

745
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,920
I was merely anxious at the moment!

746
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:14,400
Father, please rescind your decree!

747
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,360
Do you want Jiang Si

748
00:33:16,360 --> 00:33:17,080
to die for your sake?

749
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:18,400
Baoping.

750
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:21,520
How many days are left
until the wedding?

751
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,360
Your Majesty,

752
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:24,240
there are four more days to go.

753
00:33:24,280 --> 00:33:24,760
All right.

754
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,040
Once the time is up,

755
00:33:26,840 --> 00:33:27,760
the wedding shall be held as planned!

756
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:29,320
Father!

757
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:29,920
Father!

758
00:33:30,080 --> 00:33:30,600
Father!

759
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:32,240
Father, I don't want this!

760
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,320
I'm not willing to do this!

761
00:33:33,440 --> 00:33:35,600
Father, please rescind your decree!

762
00:33:35,600 --> 00:33:37,920
Your Highness, please let go!

763
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:38,800
Father!

764
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:41,160
I beg you, Your Highness, let go!

765
00:33:42,080 --> 00:33:42,760
Father.

766
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,320
Do you think

767
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:47,800
that's enough to make me submit?

768
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,480
I will never accept it

769
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:52,960
over my dead body!

770
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:54,440
Really?

771
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:56,680
Fine.

772
00:33:58,120 --> 00:33:59,440
I'll grant you your wish.

773
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,320
Well,

774
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,480
I can be a carefree prince.

775
00:34:17,719 --> 00:34:19,040
We'll just shut the world out,

776
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:21,120
live our own lives,

777
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:23,000
and find our freedom.

778
00:34:26,679 --> 00:34:28,080
I fear that fate won't be so kind.

779
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:50,000
Miss Jiang!

780
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,120
Long Dan, how is it?

781
00:34:52,199 --> 00:34:52,880
Have you heard anything?

782
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,360
Chief breached
five palace gates in a row.

783
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:55,480
He tried to resist the imperial decree.

784
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:56,800
How is he now?

785
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:57,720
Now, he's kneeling

786
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:58,720
in front of Tiande Hall.

787
00:34:58,960 --> 00:35:00,360
He said he would rather die
than accept the marriage.

788
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:02,320
What did His Majesty say?

789
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:04,640
He said

790
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,040
he would grant his wish.

791
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:09,760
- Miss Jiang?
- My Lady!

792
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:17,940
[Eternal Joy and Serenity]

793
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:20,280
Your Majesty.

794
00:35:21,200 --> 00:35:23,400
I've instructed the kitchen

795
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:25,040
to prepare your favorite dishes

796
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:26,920
and food that relieves heatiness.

797
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:29,160
If you're trying
to make a plea for Yu Jin,

798
00:35:30,040 --> 00:35:31,360
you may stop.

799
00:35:33,160 --> 00:35:33,880
Let's have our meal.

800
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:40,800
The imperial palace
will hold the Floral Banquet soon.

801
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,280
By then,

802
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:44,200
I'll come up with a way
to send you the invitation.

803
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:45,760
During the banquet,

804
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,600
I'll announce

805
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:48,440
to everyone

806
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,920
that you're the one I want to marry.

807
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,640
I'll win the Floral Banquet.

808
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,320
Your beloved

809
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:56,720
can only be me.

810
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:28,560
Jin,

811
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:31,360
you don't need to do this.

812
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:38,040
Mingyue is a princess.

813
00:36:39,160 --> 00:36:40,720
She's marrying
into your family as a co-wife

814
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:42,200
alongside a count's daughter.

815
00:36:42,640 --> 00:36:44,920
That's a great deal
of grievances for her.

816
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,920
I didn't let Mingyue

817
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,120
replace Jiang Si.

818
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:51,920
I allowed you
to be together with Jiang Si.

819
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,200
Why can't you

820
00:36:54,200 --> 00:36:55,840
just fulfill my wish

821
00:36:56,520 --> 00:36:58,320
and marry Mingyue
like the good boy you are?

822
00:36:58,720 --> 00:37:00,000
Aunt, according to you,

823
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:02,440
it's as if I'm begging her

824
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,280
to be married to me.

825
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:05,600
Whether or not I wish to get married

826
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:06,440
or whom I marry,

827
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:07,640
that's my freedom.

828
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:09,640
I don't need you to grant me my wish.

829
00:37:11,160 --> 00:37:13,520
You grew up
in a boorish land since young.

830
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:15,640
That's why you have a wild nature.

831
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:18,960
Let me give you a reminder.

832
00:37:20,160 --> 00:37:21,840
No one born into the imperial family

833
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:25,120
is free.

834
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:28,000
Each of us restrains one another

835
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:29,080
and acts under orders.

836
00:37:30,160 --> 00:37:31,240
Even Brother himself

837
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:33,280
can't do whatever he likes,

838
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:36,400
let alone a prince like you.

839
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:39,520
This is the price

840
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:40,760
you need to pay

841
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:43,120
for enjoying
a luxurious life in Ling'an.

842
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:47,920
If so, Princess Royal,
whose orders were you following

843
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:50,080
when you changed
other people's destinies?

844
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,200
What nonsense are you talking about?

845
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,640
You poisoned the Countess of Dongping.

846
00:37:54,080 --> 00:37:55,600
Now, you wanted to poison Jiang Si.

847
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:57,640
Whose orders were you following?

848
00:37:58,400 --> 00:37:59,880
You're second to none

849
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:00,880
other than His Majesty himself.

